OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,FThe manager of Scotland's highest
OL,8,Fdistillery has expressed pride at his
OL,9,Fteam's unbroken record of keeping
OL,10,Foperations running amid the heaviest
OL,11,Fwinter snowfalls.
OL,13,FDalwhinnie Distillery sits at around
OL,14,F1,300ft above sea level in the
OL,15,FCairngorms National Park in the heart
OL,16,Fof the Highlands.
