OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,FManager John Hart, 60, said the six-
OL,8,Fstrong operations team is well
OL,9,Fprepared for what the rest of the
OL,10,Fwinter might bring, as he described
OL,11,Fthe annual challenge of keeping whisky
OL,12,Fproduction going when the site is
OL,13,Fblanketed in snow.
OL,15,F"We obviously get probably more
OL,16,Fsnowfall than most parts of Scotland
OL,17,Fin terms of being a village around
OL,18,Fabout 1,300ft up, so it definitely
OL,19,Fpresents operational challenges when
OL,20,Fwe get the snowfall," he said.
