OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,F"The site has to run. We have to
OL,8,Fenable vehicles to get in with
OL,9,Fdeliveries of raw materials and we've
OL,10,Fgot collections of output being taken
OL,11,Faway.
OL,13,F"All my operators are really trained
OL,14,Fand skilled at using a snow plough.
OL,15,FIt's amazing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
