OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,F"Before I came here, I worked all my
OL,8,Flife in big towns and cities and
OL,9,Fwhenever there's snowfall in a built-
OL,10,Fup place everything grinds to a halt,
OL,11,Fand half of the workforce can't get to
OL,12,Fwork etc, but here I just have this
OL,13,Famazing team of operators who, no
OL,14,Fmatter what, they turn up and we get
OL,15,Fthe site fit and safe to allow us to
OL,16,Foperate normally.
OL,26,@oD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/10
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
