PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F305A1767320993
OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,F"It can be really challenging in the
OL,8,Fwinter months, but I think everybody
OL,9,Fhere just has a mindset that this
OL,10,Fcomes with the territory and we just
OL,11,Fmake sure that we're as prepared and
OL,12,Fresilient as we can be.
OL,14,F"I've been here seven years now and,
OL,15,Ftouch wood, I've not had to stop a
OL,16,Fsingle day of production because of
OL,17,Fsnow or bad weather."
