OL,7,FMr Hart, who is originally from
OL,8,FKilmarnock, spent most of his working
OL,9,Flife in West Yorkshire prior taking on
OL,10,Fthe job in the Highlands.
OL,12,F"I had a real desire to get a
OL,13,Fdifferent life experience," he said.
OL,15,F"Me and my wife Sally had been coming
OL,16,Fon holidays to Scotland and when the
OL,17,FDalwhinnie position came up, it just
OL,18,Fseemed to offer such a different life
OL,19,Fexperience.
OL,26,@tD@AOUuD@[O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/10
