OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,F"I'd spent all my life living in towns
OL,8,Fand cities and that was the big
OL,9,Fattraction for me. Of course, it was
OL,10,Falso a bonus that it was the whisky
OL,11,Findustry and all the emotion that we
OL,12,Fas Scottish people feel towards our
OL,13,Fnational drink.
OL,15,F"And so it was all of those components
OL,16,Fcoming together that made it a real
OL,17,Fattractive option for me.
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOU
