OL,3,CScotland's highest distillery proud of
OL,4,Cunbroken record of operating in
OL,5,Csnowfalls
OL,7,F"We live on the site, so we live
OL,8,Fthrough the winter experience as well.
OL,9,FIt's not that I travel back to
OL,10,FEdinburgh or Glasgow at the weekend
OL,11,Fand miss out.
OL,13,F"So, for us, it's been an amazing life
OL,14,Fexperience. And, yeah, when that
OL,15,Fsnowfall comes as a resident, then you
OL,16,Fhave to also be prepared, make sure
OL,17,Fthat the fridge is full. And, you
OL,18,Fknow, if you can't get out for a day
OL,19,For two, then make sure it's something
OL,20,Fthat you can be relaxed about and not
OL,21,Fworry."
