OL,7,FHe added: "I think you have to very
OL,8,Fmuch come with a mindset that don't
OL,9,Fmoan about the weather, because that's
OL,10,Fthe trade-off for all the beauty and
OL,11,Feverything else that this place
OL,12,Foffers."
OL,14,FThe distillery's water source is
OL,15,Flocated at an even greater height,
OL,16,Ffrom a loch sitting at 2,000ft up in
OL,17,Fthe Drumochter Hills that is topped up
OL,18,Fwith snow melt through the winter
OL,19,Fmonths.
