OL,7,FThe near-freezing temperature of the
OL,8,Fwater used in the distilling process
OL,9,Fat this time of year is credited with
OL,10,Fgiving Dalwhinnie Winter's Gold single
OL,11,Fmalt a distinctive taste.
OL,13,F"That's probably the key
OL,14,Fcharacteristic of the Winter's Gold
OL,15,Fbecause it's being exposed to the same
OL,16,Fextreme conditions that we experience
OL,17,Fthrough those winter months," said Mr
OL,18,FHart.
